# LOOP_QUEUE — {{LOOP_NAME}}

Work queue and source of truth. The harness processes unchecked `- [ ]` items top to bottom,
runs builder/verifier on each, commits on PASS, and flips it to `- [x]`. A unit that escalates
stops the queue until a human resolves it.

Each entry: the task, its acceptance pointer, and (the harness maintains) status + FAIL count.

